        <mxCell id="J8TLRwCM1L9d4Ld9fmev-24" parent="1" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 30px;&quot;&gt;Infrastructure Description&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 26px;&quot;&gt;The platform runs on a cloud infrastructure.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 26px;&quot;&gt;The Web App is served from a Web Server, the Backend API runs on a App Server, data is stored on a Database Server, video files are stored in Object Storage and content is delivered via CDN Edge Server.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" vertex="1">
